Message: Hi, I’m the NewsBreak Ad Assistant. How can I help?
The user completes the submission of the form
My account hasn't been released yet. Is there any estimate?

Hi André, if your account is pending due to business verification, please ensure you have provided all necessary details. You can email adsupport@newsbreak.com with the subject line: Business Verification and include your company's full address, legal entity name, EHID or DUNS number, primary contact person's name, phone number, and business URL. Once we receive this information, we'll conduct a thorough review and update you on your account status. If you've already submitted these details, it typically takes a few days for our team to process the verification. Let me know if you need any more help!
